<div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-stone-200 p-5 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
  <p class="flex-1 min-w-64 text-stone-700">
    <% case verification.overall_verdict %>
    <% when "fail" %>
      Fix the failed checks above before filing — each one cites the rule it
      breaks, so your designer knows exactly what to change.
    <% when "needs_review" %>
      The flagged items are judgment calls a reviewing agent will weigh. File
      when you are confident, or adjust the label first.
    <% when "request_retake" %>
      Retake the photo and re-check before filing — an unreadable image will
      stall your application at TTB.
    <% else %>
      This label is ready to file.
    <% end %>
  </p>
  <%= button_to "Submit to TTB", label_application_submission_path(application),
        class: "rounded-lg bg-stone-900 text-white px-5 py-2.5 font-medium hover:bg-stone-700 cursor-pointer" %>
</div>
